casebody.data:
PEOPLE
v.
ARCHULETA S218610 Supreme Court of California September 21, 2016

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 4/2. Review in the above-captioned matter, which was granted and held for People v. Sanchez (2016) 63 Cal.4th 665, 204 Cal.Rptr.3d 102, 374 P.3d 320, is hereby dismissed. (Cal. Rules of Court, Rule 8.528(b).) Defendant's request for a stay or further briefing is denied.
